on\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg will provide man-on-the-street interviews, while Clarkson and Manning will host the opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"score\": 0.9998751862015751, \"rank\": 0.00011855571811402496, \"text\": \"Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeremy_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fallon will host the closing ceremony alongside Mike Tirico, NFL play-by-play announcer on NBC'sSunday Night Football.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Tirico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC is aiming for more than 20% of Olympics viewership to come from the Peacock stream\\u00ading platform.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1288, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 0.9988412929821053, \"rank\": 0.0010797456413334232, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whether they are watching linear or digital, we do not really care,\\\" Dan Lovinger, the NBC ad sales executive,saidtoVariety.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 0.9988412929821053, \"rank\": 0.0010797456413334232, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We mon\\u00adetize all platforms.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very confident that this will be the most supported Olympic Games of all time - in dollars.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what we count.\\\"\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond the broadcast, the games have been dealing with their own organizational concerns in getting the event prepared in Paris.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1788, \"end\": 1793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999480767214, \"rank\": 5.192332788118837e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently, a water protection organization cautioned swimmers about thedangerous level of bacteriain a main competitive swimming waterway.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CLICK HERE TO READ MORE FROM THE WASHINGTON EXAMINER  Organizers also told athletes in February that there will be no air conditioning in the eco-friendly athletic village.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Examiner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"THE WASHINGTON EXAMINER\", 